Package: pyrex-py%type_pkg[python]
Version: 0.9.8.5
Revision: 1
Distribution: (%type_pkg[python] = 23) 10.4, (%type_pkg[python] = 24) 10.4, (%type_pkg[python] = 24) 10.5
